  <entry>
    <title>JavaScript notes</title>
    <url>/2022/07/20/JavaScript%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="基本语法"><a href="#基本语法" class="headerlink" title="基本语法"></a>基本语法</h1><h2 id="位置"><a href="#位置" class="headerlink" title="位置"></a>位置</h2><p>一般放在<code>&lt;script&gt;&lt;/script&gt;里面</code>，script一般放在body的末尾，但如果js代码中有定义<code>&lt;body&gt;</code>下直接调用的函数，那么js代码必须放在head</p>
<p>可以外部化: src=”xxx.js”就可以了</p>
<p>JavaScript伪协议：</p>
<p><code>&lt;a href=&quot;JavaScript:window.alert(&quot;你好，世界!&quot;);&gt;</code></p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="变量的声明"><a href="#变量的声明" class="headerlink" title="变量的声明"></a>变量的声明</h2><p>var msg = ‘Hello, world!’;</p>
<p>console.log(msg);</p>
<p>其实不用var也会隐式的声明</p>
<p>var和let是有区别的，var允许重复声明一个变量，用后来的覆盖前面的，但是let不允许</p>
<p>let能够更细致地管理变量的有效范围</p>
<p>申明常量可以用const</p>
<h2 id="数据类型"><a href="#数据类型" class="headerlink" title="数据类型"></a>数据类型</h2><p>JavaScript是弱类型的语言，所以把一个数值赋给一个字符串变量也是可以的</p>
<p>而且JavaScript中没有字符串和字符类型的区别</p>
<h2 id="模板字符串"><a href="#模板字符串" class="headerlink" title="模板字符串"></a>模板字符串</h2><p>可以把变量嵌入字符串中，比如变量是name<br>let str = <code>你好呀，$&#123;name&#125;</code>;<br>console.log(str);</p>
<h2 id="相等运算符"><a href="#相等运算符" class="headerlink" title="相等运算符"></a>相等运算符</h2><p>== 比较基本类型时，基本上只看内容，比较引用类型时，即使内容完全相同，只要地址不同就不会判定为相等</p>
<h2 id="一致运算符"><a href="#一致运算符" class="headerlink" title="一致运算符"></a>一致运算符</h2><p>===会判断数据类型是否相同</p>
<h2 id="删除delete"><a href="#删除delete" class="headerlink" title="删除delete"></a>删除delete</h2><ol>
<li>删除数组中的元素时，只删除对应的元素，后面的元素会提上来（但索引号不发生改变）</li>
<li>删除属性时也只删除属性本身，属性参照的对象不会被删除</li>
<li>显示声明的对象不能删除</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="返回类型"><a href="#返回类型" class="headerlink" title="返回类型"></a>返回类型</h2><p>用typeof</p>
<h2 id="循环"><a href="#循环" class="headerlink" title="循环"></a>循环</h2><p>for in</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> data = [ <span class="string">&#x27;apple&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;orange&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;banana&#x27;</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">var</span> key <span class="keyword">in</span> data)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(data[key]);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然而for in并不能保证处理的顺序，它只用于操作关联数组（对象），枚举还是用for或者for of</p>
<p>for in语句中，给虚拟变量传的值是键名，而for of枚举的是数组的值本身</p>
<h2 id="处理异常"><a href="#处理异常" class="headerlink" title="处理异常"></a>处理异常</h2><h3 id="try-catch-finally语句"><a href="#try-catch-finally语句" class="headerlink" title="try catch finally语句"></a>try catch finally语句</h3><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">try</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	i=i*j;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;<span class="keyword">catch</span>(e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(e.<span class="property">message</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;<span class="keyword">finally</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;处理完成了&#x27;</span>)；</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后我们就可以看到 </p>
<p>j is not defined</p>
<p>处理完成了</p>
<p>如果没有发生异常的话就会跳过catch语句，但无论如何finally语句都会被执行。注意tcf语句开销很大，一般不要滥用</p>
<h3 id="throw语句"><a href="#throw语句" class="headerlink" title="throw语句"></a>throw语句</h3><p>可以直接放在try里面</p>
<p>格式： throw </p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> number = <span class="number">5</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">// user-defined throw statement</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Error</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;This is the throw&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">catch</span>(error) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;An error caught&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>( number + <span class="number">8</span> &gt; <span class="number">10</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// statements to handle exceptions</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;Error message: &#x27;</span> + error); </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;Error resolved&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// cannot handle the exception</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// rethrow the exception</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Error</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;The value is low&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>new error也可以换成别的</p>
<div class="table-container">
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th style="text-align:left">对象</th>
<th style="text-align:left">错误的原因</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">EvalError</td>
<td style="text-align:left">不正确的eval函数</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">RangeErro</td>
<td style="text-align:left">设定的值超过了允许范围</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">ReferenceErro</td>
<td style="text-align:left">访问没有声明的变量</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">SyntaxErro</td>
<td style="text-align:left">语法错误</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">TypeError</td>
<td style="text-align:left">设定的值不是预期的类型</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">URIError</td>
<td style="text-align:left">错误的URI</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 id="异步加载"><a href="#异步加载" class="headerlink" title="异步加载"></a>异步加载</h2><p>避免加载脚本用的时间过于长，读取完后再执行</p>
<p><code>&lt;script src=&quot;lib.js&quot; async&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code></p>
<p>如果多个js文件中存在调用关系</p>
<p>可以用defer属性，指定在文档的解析完成之后再执行脚本的属性</p>
<h1 id="内置对象"><a href="#内置对象" class="headerlink" title="内置对象"></a>内置对象</h1><p>JavaScript会将null之外的对象全部视为true</p>
<p>原则上基本数据类型应该避免用new运算符实例化</p>
<p><a href="https://www.runoob.com/js/js-obj-number.html">Number</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.runoob.com/jsref/jsref-obj-string.html">String</a></p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>git常见问题的解决办法</title>
    <url>/2022/07/18/git%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Failed-to-connect-to-github-com-port-443-Timed-out"><a href="#Failed-to-connect-to-github-com-port-443-Timed-out" class="headerlink" title="Failed to connect to github.com port 443: Timed out"></a>Failed to connect to github.com port 443: Timed out</h1><p>先取消代理再设置代理</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global --unset http.proxy</span><br><span class="line">git config --global --unset https.proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy http://127.0.0.1:1080</span><br><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy https://127.0.0.1:1080</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="does-not-have-a-commit-checked-out"><a href="#does-not-have-a-commit-checked-out" class="headerlink" title="does not have a commit checked out"></a>does not have a commit checked out</h1><p>哪个文件夹报的错，删掉那个文件夹的.git</p>
<h1 id="fatal-unable-to-access-xxxxx-OpenSSL-SSL-read-Connection-was-reset-errno-10054"><a href="#fatal-unable-to-access-xxxxx-OpenSSL-SSL-read-Connection-was-reset-errno-10054" class="headerlink" title="fatal: unable to access xxxxx OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was reset, errno 10054"></a>fatal: unable to access xxxxx OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was reset, errno 10054</h1><p><code>git config --global http.sslVerify &quot;false&quot;</code></p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
